    "updated_at": "2016-10-07T01:01:56Z",
    "body": "I wonder if its possible to give electron apps a kind of \"pseudo origin\" like a bundle identifier that gives them proper sandboxing. This would allow the credential API to plug into the credential storage manager of the OS. For example, keychain on OSX. Does this make sense?\n"
